text: @chrislhayes @AOC @BernieSanders @JoeBiden @ewarren @MichaelBloomber @PeteButtigieg @amyklobuchar Coronavirus is going to have a huge impact on voter turnout esp in urban/high density areas. This is a major threat to 2020 election. Do you have an actionable plan, we need to hear from you now.
